{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1325,"text":"Let's say you despise"},{"time":3587,"text":"Western democracy."},{"time":6592,"text":"Democracy, in all its trappings,"},{"time":8828,"text":"free elections, town halls,"},{"time":11515,"text":"endless debates about\nthe proper role of government."},{"time":14375,"text":"Too messy,"},{"time":15732,"text":"too unpredictable,"},{"time":16912,"text":"too constraining for your taste."},{"time":19711,"text":"And the way these democracies\nband together and lecture everyone else"},{"time":23985,"text":"about individual rights and freedoms --"},{"time":26300,"text":"it gets under your skin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29380,"text":"So what to do about it?"},{"time":32141,"text":"You can call out the hypocrisy\nand failures of Western democracies"},{"time":36703,"text":"and explain how your way is better,"},{"time":39956,"text":"but that's never really worked for you."},{"time":42716,"text":"What if you could get the people"},{"time":45416,"text":"whose support is the very foundation\nof these democracies"},{"time":48580,"text":"to start questioning the system?"},{"time":52442,"text":"Make the idea occur in their own minds"},{"time":54914,"text":"that democracy and its institutions\nare failing them,"},{"time":59050,"text":"their elite are corrupt puppet masters"},{"time":61334,"text":"and the country they knew is in free fall."},{"time":65783,"text":"To do that,"},{"time":67081,"text":"you'll need to infiltrate\nthe information spheres"},{"time":70103,"text":"of these democracies."},{"time":71429,"text":"You'll need to turn\ntheir most powerful asset --"},{"time":75154,"text":"an open mind --"},{"time":77083,"text":"into their greatest vulnerability."},{"time":80088,"text":"You'll need people to question the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84102,"text":"Now, you'll be familiar of hacking\nand leaks that happened in 2016."},{"time":88868,"text":"One was the Democratic\nNational Committee's networks,"},{"time":91714,"text":"and the personal email\naccounts of its staff,"},{"time":94569,"text":"later released on WikiLeaks."},{"time":97024,"text":"After that, various online personas,"},{"time":99374,"text":"like a supposed Romanian cybercriminal\nwho didn't speak Romanian,"},{"time":104278,"text":"aggressively pushed news\nof these leaks to journalists."},{"time":108991,"text":"The media took the bait."},{"time":110811,"text":"They were consumed by how much\nthe DNC hated Bernie."},{"time":114918,"text":"At the time, it was that narrative\nthat far outshined the news"},{"time":119182,"text":"that a group of Russian government\nsponsored hackers"},{"time":122546,"text":"who we called \"Advanced\nPersistent Threat 28,\""},{"time":125803,"text":"or \"APT28\" for short,"},{"time":128408,"text":"was carrying out\nthese operations against the US."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132192,"text":"And there was no shortage of evidence."},{"time":134984,"text":"This group of Russian government hackers\nhadn't just appeared out of nowhere"},{"time":138726,"text":"in 2016."},{"time":139914,"text":"We had started tracking\nthis group back in 2014."},{"time":143095,"text":"And the tools that APT28 used\nto compromise its victims' networks"},{"time":148000,"text":"demonstrated a thoughtful,\nwell-resourced effort"},{"time":151617,"text":"that had taken place for now over a decade"},{"time":154467,"text":"in Moscow's time zone"},{"time":155990,"text":"from about 9 am to 6 pm."},{"time":159095,"text":"APT28 loved to prey on the emails\nand contacts of journalists in Chechnya,"},{"time":164201,"text":"the Georgian government,\neastern European defense attach√©s --"},{"time":167732,"text":"all targets with an undeniable interest\nto the Russian government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171797,"text":"We weren't the only ones onto this."},{"time":173781,"text":"Governments, research teams\nacross the world,"},{"time":177222,"text":"were coming to similar conclusions"},{"time":179153,"text":"and observing the same\ntypes of operations."},{"time":182332,"text":"But what Russia was doing in 2016"},{"time":185464,"text":"went far beyond espionage."},{"time":188060,"text":"The DNC hack was just one of many\nwhere stolen data was posted online"},{"time":194702,"text":"accompanied by a sensational narrative,"},{"time":196980,"text":"then amplified in social media"},{"time":198942,"text":"for lightning-speed adoption by the media."},{"time":204836,"text":"This didn't ring the alarm bells"},{"time":207402,"text":"that a nation-state was trying\nto interfere with the credibility"},{"time":211917,"text":"of another's internal affairs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213865,"text":"So why, collectively,\ndid we not see this coming?"},{"time":219111,"text":"Why did it take months\nbefore Americans understood"},{"time":223017,"text":"that they were under a state-sponsored\ninformation attack?"},{"time":228456,"text":"The easy answer is politics."},{"time":230119,"text":"The Obama Administration was caught\nin a perfect catch-22."},{"time":234066,"text":"By raising the specter that the Russian\ngovernment was interfering"},{"time":238488,"text":"in the US presidential campaign,"},{"time":240604,"text":"the Administration risked appearing\nto meddle in the campaign itself."},{"time":245992,"text":"But the better answer, I think,"},{"time":248071,"text":"is that the US and the West\nwere utterly unequipped"},{"time":251948,"text":"to recognize and respond\nto a modern information operation,"},{"time":256626,"text":"despite the fact that the US\nhad wielded information"},{"time":261762,"text":"with devastating success\nin an era not so long ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266284,"text":"Look, so while the US and the West\nspent the last 20 years"},{"time":270202,"text":"caught up in cybersecurity --"},{"time":271780,"text":"what networks to harden,"},{"time":273299,"text":"which infrastructure to deem critical,"},{"time":275632,"text":"how to set up armies of cyber warriors\nand cyber commands --"},{"time":279649,"text":"Russia was thinking in far more\nconsequential terms."},{"time":285322,"text":"Before the first iPhone\neven hit the shelf,"},{"time":288673,"text":"the Russian government understood\nthe risks and the opportunity"},{"time":293170,"text":"that technology provided"},{"time":294619,"text":"and the inter-communication\nand instant communication it provided us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300491,"text":"As our realities are increasingly\nbased on the information"},{"time":303732,"text":"that we're consuming\nat the palm of our hand"},{"time":306112,"text":"and from the news feeds\nthat we're scanning"},{"time":308389,"text":"and the hashtags and stories\nthat we see trending,"},{"time":311379,"text":"the Russian government\nwas the first to recognize"},{"time":314330,"text":"how this evolution"},{"time":316229,"text":"had turned your mind into the most\nexploitable device on the planet."},{"time":322954,"text":"And your mind is particularly exploitable"},{"time":325442,"text":"if you're accustomed\nto an unfettered flow of information,"},{"time":329241,"text":"now increasingly curated\nto your own tastes."},{"time":335244,"text":"This panorama of information\nthat's so interesting to you"},{"time":338159,"text":"gives a state, or anyone for that matter,\na perfect back door into your mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344978,"text":"It's this new brand of state-sponsored\ninformation operations"},{"time":348680,"text":"that can be that much more successful,"},{"time":350839,"text":"more insidious,"},{"time":352165,"text":"and harder for the target audience --\nthat includes the media --"},{"time":356275,"text":"to decipher and characterize."},{"time":358702,"text":"If you can get a hashtag\ntrending on Twitter,"},{"time":360919,"text":"or chum the waters with fake news"},{"time":364058,"text":"directed to audiences\nprimed to receive it,"},{"time":366523,"text":"or drive journalists to dissect\nterabytes of email"},{"time":369424,"text":"for a cent of impropriety --"},{"time":371423,"text":"all tactics used in Russian operations --"},{"time":374089,"text":"then you've got a shot at effectively\ncamouflaging your operations"},{"time":378404,"text":"in the mind of your target."},{"time":381867,"text":"This is what Russia's long called\n\"reflexive control.\""},{"time":386849,"text":"It's the ability to use\ninformation on someone else"},{"time":390655,"text":"so that they make a decision"},{"time":392863,"text":"on their own accord"},{"time":394438,"text":"that's favorable to you."},{"time":398291,"text":"This is nation-state-grade image control\nand perception management,"},{"time":402394,"text":"and it's conducted by any means,"},{"time":404736,"text":"with any tools, network-based\nor otherwise, that will achieve it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409811,"text":"Take this for another example."},{"time":411265,"text":"In early February 2014, a few weeks\nbefore Russia would invade Crimea,"},{"time":416242,"text":"a phone call is posted on YouTube."},{"time":418495,"text":"In it, there's two US diplomats."},{"time":420894,"text":"They sound like they're playing\nkingmaker in Ukraine,"},{"time":424112,"text":"and worse, they curse the EU\nfor its lack of speed and leadership"},{"time":427579,"text":"in resolving the crisis."},{"time":430067,"text":"The media covers the phone call,"},{"time":432550,"text":"and then the ensuing diplomatic backlash"},{"time":437183,"text":"leaves Washington and Europe reeling."},{"time":440962,"text":"And it creates a fissured response\nand a feckless attitude"},{"time":445065,"text":"towards Russia's land grab in Ukraine."},{"time":448118,"text":"Mission accomplished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450648,"text":"So while hacked phone calls\nand emails and networks"},{"time":454052,"text":"keep grabbing the headlines,"},{"time":456122,"text":"the real operations are the ones"},{"time":458780,"text":"that are influencing\nthe decisions you make"},{"time":461612,"text":"and the opinions you hold,"},{"time":463454,"text":"all in the service of a nation-state's\nstrategic interest."},{"time":467944,"text":"This is power in the information age."},{"time":471527,"text":"And this information is all\nthat much more seductive,"},{"time":474995,"text":"all that much easier to take\nat face value and pass on,"},{"time":478806,"text":"when it's authentic."},{"time":480877,"text":"Who's not interested in the truth\nthat's presented in phone calls and emails"},{"time":486295,"text":"that were never intended\nfor public consumption?"},{"time":490241,"text":"But how meaningful is that truth"},{"time":492019,"text":"if you don't know why\nit's being revealed to you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495966,"text":"We must recognize that this place\nwhere we're increasingly living,"},{"time":500178,"text":"which we've quaintly termed \"cyberspace,\""},{"time":502487,"text":"isn't defined by ones and zeroes,"},{"time":504717,"text":"but by information\nand the people behind it."},{"time":508828,"text":"This is far more than a network\nof computers and devices."},{"time":511995,"text":"This is a network composed of minds"},{"time":515171,"text":"interacting with computers and devices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518950,"text":"And for this network,"},{"time":522628,"text":"there's no encryption,\nthere's no firewall,"},{"time":526033,"text":"no two-factor authentication,"},{"time":527780,"text":"no password complex enough to protect you."},{"time":531568,"text":"What you have for defense"},{"time":534006,"text":"is far stronger, it's more adaptable,\nit's always running the latest version."},{"time":539310,"text":"It's the ability to think critically:"},{"time":542259,"text":"call out falsehood,"},{"time":544002,"text":"press for the facts."},{"time":546802,"text":"And above all, you must have the courage"},{"time":551019,"text":"to unflinchingly pursue the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555752,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}